"smart_sources:000 Zettelkasten/It is a frequent occurrence for tumor antigens to be expressed at low levels on the outer surface, posing challenges to the effective signalling of CAR-T cells..md": {"path":"000 Zettelkasten/It is a frequent occurrence for tumor antigens to be expressed at low levels on the outer surface, posing challenges to the effective signalling of CAR-T cells..md","class_name":"SmartSource","history":[{"blocks":{"000 Zettelkasten/It is a frequent occurrence for tumor antigens to be expressed at low levels on the outer surface, posing challenges to the effective signalling of CAR-T cells..md#":true,"000 Zettelkasten/It is a frequent occurrence for tumor antigens to be expressed at low levels on the outer surface, posing challenges to the effective signalling of CAR-T cells..md#It is a frequent occurrence for tumour antigens to be expressed at low levels on the outer surface, posing challenges to the effective signalling of CAR-T cells. [[The split-receptor method helps to maintain CART-T specificity by using a negative feedback signaling to prevent excessive T-cell activity and minimize proinflammatory damage to the patient.]] can also be used here to enhance T-cell sensitivity to antigen targets. This can be done by adding costimulatory receptor that activate the immune system.{1}":true,"000 Zettelkasten/It is a frequent occurrence for tumor antigens to be expressed at low levels on the outer surface, posing challenges to the effective signalling of CAR-T cells..md#References":true},"mtime":1709479529554,"size":643,"hash":"e9dba33a95c94adc2b128011ec62a01c44781cc70cc0eb3328a11a12e9fdae4d"}],"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.00743001,-0.0117263,-0.02182915,0.03709082,0.03817211,-0.00529941,0.0332444,-0.02989112,-0.00569299,-0.00314213,-0.01209192,-0.00939969,-0.02772489,-0.04749471,0.02519028,-0.00607188,0.03281828,-0.00903818,0.00426451,-0.00783896,0.03037512,-0.00812434,-0.00348071,0.02796173,-0.05256224,-0.0199353,0.00868298,0.0